    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed their required gradation levels. The single below-required factor (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is accepted based on compensating evidence: inter-laboratory coefficient of variation below 4%, tight E/uval values across all three QoIs, and the fact that ASTM F1717 prescribes a single standardized test configuration as the regulatory benchmark. The package is submitted under ProfileMinimal; the cryptographic signature workflow is pending organizational PKI provisioning and will be applied prior to regulatory submission. The hash field provides content integrity verification in the interim.",
